import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { useRouter } from 'next/router' import styles from './styles/header.module.css' import { Button } from 'antd' import { UserOutlined, ShoppingCartOutlined } from '@ant-design/icons' import firebase from '../firebaseConfig' const Header = () => { const router = useRouter() const [toggleNavBar, setToggleNavBar] = useState(true) const [user, setUser] = useState(null) useEffect(() => { async function getUser() { let user = await firebase.auth().currentUser console.log(user) return user } setUser(getUser()) }, []) const navBarStyleItem = (route, name) => { if(router.pathname === route) { return

router.push(route)}>{name}

} else { return

router.push(route)}>{name}

} } return (
{navBarStyleItem("/", "TIENDA")}
{navBarStyleItem("/nosotros", "NOSOTROS")}
{navBarStyleItem("/contacto", "CONTACTO")}
 setToggleNavBar(!toggleNavBar)}>
{toggleNavBar &&
router.push('/')} >TIENDA
router.push('/nosotros')}>NOSOTROS
router.push('/contactanos')}>CONTACTANOS
}
); } export default Header;
